import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.scatterplot(data=data, x='u', y='v')
    plt.title("What is the correlation between the 'u' and 'v' dimensions?", wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='diff', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(x=data['diff'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"Mean: {data['diff'].mean():.2f}")
    plt.axvline(x=data['diff'].median(), color='green', linestyle='--', label=f"Median: {data['diff'].median():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.title("What is the distribution of the 'diff' field?", wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('diff')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

chart = plot(data)
